Because you&#39;re using curly braces in the `map`s you need to explicitly use `return`. In addition, you&#39;ll also need to wrap your inner code in another element like a `div` or [a React fragment](https://reactjs.org/docs/fragments.html) (which I&#39;ve used here) as multiple children must be enclosed within a parent element.

